# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# DEPLOYMENT NOTES
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Local Development:
#   1. Copy this file to `.env` in the project root
#   2. Fill in your Supabase credentials from the dashboard
#   3. Run `npm run dev` or `pnpm dev`
#
# Lovable Deployment:
#   1. Go to: https://lovable.app/projects/80074ec3-bcf4-4664-b8d4-6e22f1506a17/settings
#   2. Add environment variables in the "Environment Variables" section
#   3. Add all VITE_* variables (client-side only)
#   4. Do NOT add SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY (Edge Functions get it automatically)
#
# Supabase Edge Functions:
#   - SUPABASE_URL and SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY are automatically injected
#   - No need to manually configure these for deployed functions
#   - For local function testing: create `supabase/.env` if needed
#
# Vercel/Netlify Deployment:
#   - Add all VITE_* variables in the deployment platform's env settings
#   - Edge Functions are deployed separately to Supabase
